   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,639:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 1. Executive Summary
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: This system uses 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,640:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Generalized Autoregressive Conditional Heteroskedasticity (GARCH)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,643:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  models to forecast
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,643:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: stock price volatility and identify mispriced options. The core strategy is a 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,644:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: long straddle
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,650:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  — simultaneously buying an
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,660:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: at-the-money (ATM) call and put option — on stocks where the GARCH model predicts that future realized volatility
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,661:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: will exceed the market
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,661:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,662:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s current implied volatility.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,662:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Key characteristics:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,663:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,664:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Model:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,667:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  GJR-GARCH(1,1,1) with Student-t innovations
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,667:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,668:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Strategy:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,669:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Long straddle, 10 trading day hold
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,669:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,669:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Budget:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,670:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  $150 per trade
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,670:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,671:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Universe:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,672:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  42 affordable tickers (stocks priced ~$1–$30)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,672:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,673:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Execution:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,673:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Webull OpenAPI with automated order placement
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,674:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,674:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Risk control:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,675:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Auto-close at +10% return; 10-day maximum hold
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,676:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 2. System Architecture
