   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,948:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 8.3 Auto-Close Monitor
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,949:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: A background daemon (
