   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,950:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ) runs continuously:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,950:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,950:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Market hours (9:30 AM – 4:00 PM ET):
