   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,965:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  If any straddle
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,966:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,966:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s total unrealized P
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,967:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: &
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,967:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: L ≥ +10%, auto-sell both legs
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,974:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,975:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Logging:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,975:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  All checks logged to 
