   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,978:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 9. Risk Management
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,979:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 9.1 Position Sizing
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,979:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,980:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Maximum 90% of capital deployed per trade
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,980:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,981:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Budget capped at $150 per trade
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,981:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,982:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Commission-aware sizing ($0.65/contract/leg)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,983:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 9.2 Diversification
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,983:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The scanner ranks 42 tickers but executes only the 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,984:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: single best signal
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,985:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: . This concentrates risk but maximizes edge on
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,985:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: the highest-conviction opportunity.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,986:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 9.3 Time-Based Risk
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,986:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,987:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 10-day maximum holding period limits exposure to prolonged theta decay
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,987:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,988:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Options selected with ~14-18 days to expiration, avoiding rapid time decay near expiry
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,989:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 9.4 Known Risks
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,989:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Risk | Mitigation |
