   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,994:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Model risk | GJR-GARCH captures asymmetry; Student-t captures fat tails |
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,995:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:02,996:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |
