   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,000:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,001:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: GARCH conditional volatility correlates 0.5–0.8 with realized volatility on validation sets across
