   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,012:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 11. Appendix: Mathematical Reference
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,012:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: A. Log Returns
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,013:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: r_t = ln(P_t / P_{t-1})
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,013:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: B. GARCH(1,1) Variance Equation
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,014:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: σ²_t = ω + α·ε²_{t-1} + β·σ²_{t-1}
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,014:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: C. GJR-GARCH(1,1,1) Variance Equation
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,015:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: σ²_t = ω + (α + γ·I_{t-1})·ε²_{t-1} + β·σ²_{t-1}
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,015:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: I_{t-1} = 1 if ε_{t-1} < 0, else 0
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,016:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: D. Annualization
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,016:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: σ_annual = σ_daily × √252
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,017:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: E. Black-Scholes Straddle Price
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,017:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Straddle = Call(S, K, T, r, σ) + Put(S, K, T, r, σ)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,018:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: F. Student-t Log-Likelihood
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,018:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ℓ(ν, σ²) = Σ [ln Γ((ν+1)/2) - ln Γ(ν/2) - ½ln(π(ν-2)σ²_t) 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,019:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:             - ((ν+1)/2)·ln(1 + ε²_t/((ν-2)σ²_t))]
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,019:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: G. AIC Model Selection
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,020:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: AIC = 2k - 2·ln(L̂)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-27 23:08:03,020:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Lower AIC = better model (balances fit vs complexity).
